flowchart TD
    Client[Client]
    Api[Host.Api]
    Corr[CorrelationIdMiddleware]
    SerilogReq[UseSerilogRequestLogging]
    ReqLife[RequestLifecycleLoggingMiddleware]
    Controller[TCodeController]
    Authz[TCodeAuthorizationService]
    BusinessDb[(BusinessDb)]
    LogDb[(LogDb)]
    FileLog[(logs/*.txt)]

    Client --> Api
    Api --> Corr
    Corr --> SerilogReq
    SerilogReq --> ReqLife
    ReqLife --> Controller
    Controller --> Authz
    Authz --> BusinessDb
    Controller --> BusinessDb
    ReqLife --> LogDb
    SerilogReq --> FileLog
    Controller --> ReqLife
    ReqLife --> Client
